RESEARCH PROJECT: A Demonstration of C-LARA
RESEARCHERS: Branislav Bédi, ChatGPT, Belinda Chiera, Cathy Chua, Neasa Ní Chiaráin, Manny Rayner, Annika Simonson, Rina Zviel-Girshin.

